properties.areaDesc: Munising to Grand Marais MI; Grand Marais to Whitefish Point MI; Marquette to Munising MI
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 14 at 10:54AM EST until January 15 at 9:00AM EST by NWS Marquette MI
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 10 to 20 kt with gusts up to 25 kt and waves
3 to 6 feet expected.

* WHERE...Marquette to Munising MI, Munising to Grand Marais MI
and Grand Marais to Whitefish Point MI.

* WHEN...From 9 PM this evening to 9 AM EST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 9 PM THIS EVENING TO 9 AM EST WEDNESDAY
